  "text": "We believe that an end-to-end strategy would dominate future part-based deep FAE algorithms, where the attributerelevant regions and the corresponding prediction can be yielded in a unified framework [CITATION_1] ). [CITATION_2] have attempted to tackle this issue, but learning a region for each attribute is cumbrous and computationally expensive. This is because several attributes might appear in the same region of a face.",
